[h1]GK Civics[/h1]

A collection of civic tweaks and additions from the GK mod suite.

[h2]Current contents[/h2]

[b]Galvanic Symbiosis (vanilla override)[/b] - removes the Infernal species_class restriction from the standard, hive, and corporate variants of Galvanic Symbiosis. Any species with the Infernals Species Pack DLC can now take the civic. The machine variant was already unrestricted in vanilla and is untouched. All other gates (DLC requirement, origin/civic exclusions, authority/ethic potential) are preserved.

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]

Conflicts with any other mod that redefines [code]civic_galvanic_symbiosis[/code], [code]civic_hive_galvanic_symbiosis[/code], or [code]civic_corporate_galvanic_symbiosis[/code]. Load this mod after such mods to win.
